## Part 1: Font Recommendations by Use Case

### Modern Tech Products (Vercel, Stripe, Figma style)

```typescript
// tokens/typography.ts
export const fontStack = {
  // Display: Bold, modern, eye-catching
  display: {
    name: "Sohne",
    fallback: "Inter, system-ui, sans-serif",
    weight: [600, 700],
    use: "Large headlines (hero, section titles)",
