## Performance Tips

✅ **DO:**
- Preconnect to Google Fonts
- Only load weights you need (400, 500, 600, 700)
- Use `display=swap` to avoid invisible text
- Use Next.js font optimization when possible
- Use CSS variables for fallbacks

❌ **DON'T:**
- Load all Google Fonts weights
- Use more than 2-3 font families
- Load fonts from multiple CDNs
- Use fancy display fonts for body text
- Forget system font fallbacks

